---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for RecipeBox AI">
  <div class="page-container">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="header">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>RecipeBox AI</p>
      </header>
      
      <div class="content">
        <div class="last-updated">
          Last Updated: December 2024
        </div>
        
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>RecipeBox AI ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application.</p>
        
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3>2.1 Information You Provide</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Email address and password when you create an account</li>
          <li><strong>Recipe Data:</strong> Recipes you save, create, or import into the app</li>
          <li><strong>User Preferences:</strong> Dietary preferences, tags, and customization settings</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>2.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> How you interact with the app (features used, time spent)</li>
          <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system version</li>
          <li><strong>Crash Reports:</strong> Technical error data to improve stability</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide and maintain the RecipeBox AI service</li>
          <li>Sync your recipes across devices</li>
          <li>Generate AI-powered nutrition insights and recipe transformations</li>
          <li>Improve app functionality and user experience</li>
          <li>Send important service-related notifications</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <p>Your data is stored securely using industry-standard encryption. Recipe data is synced via Supabase, a secure cloud database platform. We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information.</p>
        
        <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Supabase:</strong> Cloud database and authentication</li>
          <li><strong>OpenAI:</strong> AI-powered features (recipe analysis, transformations)</li>
          <li><strong>RevenueCat:</strong> Subscription management</li>
          <li><strong>Apple Sign In:</strong> Optional authentication</li>
          <li><strong>Google Sign In:</strong> Optional authentication</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Export your recipes</li>
          <li>Delete your account and all associated data</li>
          <li>Opt out of non-essential data collection</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain your data as long as your account is active. You can delete your account at any time from the app settings, which will remove all your personal data from our servers within 30 days.</p>
        
        <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>RecipeBox AI is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
        
        <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy in the app and updating the "Last Updated" date.</p>
        
        <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:hello@recipeboxai.app">hello@recipeboxai.app</a></p>
        
        <div class="back-link">
          <a href="/">← Back to Home</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-container {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B6B, #4ECDC4);
    color: white;
    padding: 40px 30px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5em;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  
  .content {
    padding: 40px 30px;
  }
  
  .last-updated {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    padding: 15px 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    border-left: 4px solid #4ECDC4;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  h2 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    font-size: 1.4em;
    margin: 30px 0 15px 0;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef;
  }
  
  h3 {
    color: #34495e;
    font-size: 1.2em;
    margin: 25px 0 12px 0;
  }
  
  p, li {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  
  ul {
    padding-left: 30px;
    margin: 15px 0;
  }
  
  a {
    color: #667eea;
  }
  
  .back-link {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
  }
  
  .back-link a {
    color: #667eea;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
